st-550 page type-page status-publish hentry"><div class="post-content"><p style="text-align: justify;">We are continually looking to add top talent to our ever-growing team. Our employees come from a blend of backgrounds, experiences and perspectives, and it is this diversity of talent that makes for a truly unique work environment. What all our employees have in common are high-caliber intellect, passion for technology, and a deep commitment to deliver market-leading solutions.</p><p style="text-align: justify;">At Kalkitech, were always looking for smart, talented individuals with diverse backgrounds who have a passion for technology and a drive to deliver the best. If this sounds like you, send in your resume to <a title="blocked::mailto:hr@kalkitech.in" href="mailto:hr@kalkitech.in">hr@kalkitech.in</a>.</p><p style="text-align: justify;">We currently have openings for the following positions in our organisation:</p><div class="container one" style="width:100%; height:auto"><ul class="responsive-accordion responsive-accordion-default bm-larger"><li><div class="responsive-accordion-head" style="background-color:#3a62a7"><span style="color:#ffffff;font-size:16px"> Senior Engineer/Technical Specialist  Embedded </span><i class="fa fa-chevron-down responsive-accordion-plus fa-fw"></i><i class="fa fa-chevron-up responsive-accordion-minus fa-fw"></i></div><div class="responsive-accordion-panel"style="background-color:;padding:px;color:;font-size:px"><p><table border="0" width="100%" cellspacing="4" cellpadding="0"><tbody><tr><td style="text-align: left;"><strong>Job Location</strong></td><td style="text-align: left;"><strong>Cochin/Bangalore</strong><br /><hr /></td></tr><tr><td style="text-align: left;"><strong>Academic Qualification</strong></td><td style="text-align: left;"><strong>B-Tech or M-Tech in Electronics and Communication</strong><br /><hr /></td></tr><tr><td style="text-align: left;"><strong>Years of Experience</strong></td><td>8+ years hands on design and development in Embedded Linux applications in C.</p><hr /></td></tr><tr><td><strong>Essential Skills</strong></td><td><ul><li>Communication related projects with emphasis on IP Networking stacks.</li><li>Experience in communication stacks like serial (RS232/485), TCP/IP, I2C, SPI.</li><li>Expertise in embedded Linux and Operating System fundamentals.</li><li>Working knowledge of embedded board bring-up firmware, bootloaders and device drivers.</li><li>Demonstrated Experience in working with tools like Subversion or equivalent, GCC tool chain, makefiles, gdb, valgrind, Bugzilla, shell scripts.</li><li>Experience with microcontroller platforms would be a plus</li></ul><hr /></td></tr><tr><td style="text-align: left;"><strong>Desired Skills</strong></td><td><ul><li>Good team player</li><li>Very good written and oral communication skills</li><li>Preference for experience in product development over full lifecycle for at least 1 product</li><li>Preference for experience in working with DevOps environments</li><li>Experience in agile product development model is a plus.</li></ul></td></tr></tbody></table></p></div></li><li><div class="responsive-accordion-head" style="background-color:#3a62a7"><span style="color:#ffffff;font-size:16px"> Senior Engineer/Technical Specialist  Java  Cloud </span><i class="fa fa-chevron-down responsive-accordion-plus fa-fw"></i><i class="fa fa-chevron-up responsive-accordion-minus fa-fw"></i></div><div class="responsive-accordion-panel"style="background-color:;padding:px;color:;font-size:px"><p><table border="0" width="100%" cellspacing="4" cellpadding="0"><tbody><tr><td style="text-align: left;"><strong>Job Location</strong></td><td style="text-align: left;"><strong>Cochin/Bangalore</strong><br /><hr /></td></tr><tr><td style="text-align: left;"><strong>Academic Qualification</strong></td><td style="text-align: left;"><strong>B-Tech/ M-Tech in Computer Science/ MCA</strong><br /><hr /></td></tr><tr><td style="text-align: left;"><strong>Year